                <p class="text-center mb-4" id="exacerbations-text">The treatment led to a major decrease in pulmonary exacerbations, acute worsening of respiratory symptoms often requiring hospitalization and intravenous antibiotics, which contribute to progressive lung damage in CF.</p>
                <div class="chart-container">
                    <canvas id="exacerbationsChart"></canvas>
                </div>
