                <p class="text-center mb-4" id="qol-text">Patient-reported outcomes, specifically the Cystic Fibrosis Questionnaire-Revised (CFQ-R) respiratory domain score, demonstrated a significant improvement in respiratory symptoms and overall quality of life, a crucial aspect of patient-centered care.</p>
